{
  "text": "Scientific RepoRts | 7:42739 | DOI: 10.1038/srep42739 regulation of chromatin remodelling [CITATION_1] 32 . For the liberated COOH-terminal fragments of the kinase, its phosphorylation may impact kinase trafficking or the function of the kinase within the nucleus.",
